- group of similar types of classes,interface & sub-package
types of packages
1. built-in packages
	eg. java.util,java.sql,java.net,java.lang,java.swing,java.awt

2. used defined packages

Advantages:
1. to categorised the classes,interface
2. provides access protection
3. removes naming collision

Note: if you import a package using *(all classes & interfaces),
 subpackages will not be imported, only classes & interfaces imported